query:
SELECT id, contactName, stopType, stopColor, contactLabels, latitude, longitude 
FROM routeWaypoints 
WHERE routeId = (SELECT id FROM routes WHERE shareToken = '308c43b5-adcf-44db-b71f-088647a80bda')
ORDER BY position;
